role_dependencies: Ensures Snap is installed on Linux systems
Ensures Homebrew is installed on MacOS systems
role_description: An Ansible role that installs jo (a command-line tool for creating JSON objects) on Linux and macOS
role_description_full_overview: [jo](https://github.com/jpmens/jo) is a free and open-source command-line tool that allows you to create JSON objects.
role_description_alt: This repository is the home of an Ansible role that installs jo (a command-line tool for creating JSON objects) on Linux and macOS.
